				<p><p>Using a Kalman filter will definitely work to estimate velocity. However you will not be able to estimate position with accuracy. This is because the position is unobservable with just encoders and an optical flow sensor. You will still be able to estimate position but the uncertainty will be unbounded.</p>
</p><br>
